Imprisoned on the other side of the universe, the mighty In Progress finds himself in a deadly gladiatorial contest that pits him against the Hulk, his former ally and fellow Avenger. In Progress's quest for survival leads him in a race against time to prevent the all-powerful Hela from destroying his home world and the Asgardian civilization.
